SPR, DGR

Creates a huge explosion dealing massive damage,

Stabs a massive bolt of lightning forword, unable

#lightning is random can miss but deal

#Ice spells are expensive but deal good damage

Creates a solid large snowflake and hurls it at

With a dark look and a blood curtling laugh Kane stabs

Kane uses his masterful skills and experience fighting
